metadata.name: Codebase Ventures Inc
metadata.description: Cypher Metaverse Inc., together with its subsidiaries, engages in identifying investments in emerging technology sectors, including blockchain ecosystem, fintech, and the metaverse. The company was formerly known as Codebase Ventures Inc. and changed its name to Cypher Metaverse Inc. in March 2022. Cypher Metaverse Inc. was incorporated in 2009 and is based in Vancouver, Canada.
